name: Rishikesh River Rafting
description:
A memory made into painting. This is from my River Rafting trip to Risikesh, India. Ganga Mata flows very rapidly here, Creating amazing white water Rafting experience . This seen is from pedestrian Bridge connecting two banks.

Medium: Acrylic on Canvas Size: 51x 36 cm Original Physical Art work available on request. Shipped anywhere in the world. visit and contact: https://tanmay.rocklaz.com/
